{
  "texts": [
    "As a result, the experimental set-up is very similar to existing studies on overt racial bias in language models 4, 7.",
    "All other aspects of the analysis (such as computing adjective association scores) were identical to the analysis for covert stereotypes.",
    "This also holds for GPT4, for which we again could not conduct the agreement analysis.",
    "We again present average results for the five language models in the main article.",
    "Results broken down for individual model versions are provided in the Supplementary Information, where we also analyse variation across prompts (Supplementary Fig. 8 and Supplementary Table 5)."
  ]
}